\f0\fs26 \cf0 There are two programs available to upload new firmwares on the MiniCommand controller. The first one is geared towards users, and is called the Patch Manager, while the second one is used to develop new firmwares and is called the Mididuino editor.\
\

\b The Patch Manager
\b0 \
The Patch Manager connects to the Ruin & Wesen website and checks if new firmwares are available. It then downloads these firmwares and presents them in an easy to browse list. Each firmware comes with its documentation, and has a list of tags describing its functionality. The Patch Manager can be downloaded at {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "http://ruinwesen.com/minicommand"}}{\fldrslt http://ruinwesen.com/minicommand}} .\
